# Calibration manifest — note: the verifier, trusted_keys.json, the
# generator, the test signed fixture, AND the test signing key are all
# PUBLIC. The test signing key is labeled `use: "test-only"` in
# trusted_keys.json; trust binding is per-kid, so production deployments
# (which will not include this kid) are unaffected. Public test artifacts
# match the existing test_view_hash.py / view_hash_fixture.yaml precedent
# and let auditors run a known-good round-trip on a fresh clone.
#
# Production signing keys (when Batch 2 generates them) MUST live outside
# this repo entirely — the server side is in ~/parallax_mcp/, not here.
# Nothing in this repo's tests/ directory is ever a production secret.

